704354f-b.title: Brooklyn: Flatlands Avenue - 40th Street (East)
704354f-b.text:
(1)
Flatlands Ave., south side, between East 40th and 41st Streets, showing the John Brown House, owned by J. Brown in 1860, and by
J. S. Brewn in 1873.
1922.
Eugene L, Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, from another angle.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
